Detect::Module - Perl module to autodetect/load at runtime other Perl modules.


INSTALLATION:

The usual procedure works:
* unzip the files to some directory
* perl Makefile.PL
* make
* su -c "make install"


DOCUMENTATION:

Just type
  man Detect::Module
after or
  perdoc Module.pm
before installing.


